Title: Sister Stella L.
Writer: Jose F. Lacaba (screenplay), Jose Almojuela (screenplay), Mike De Leon (screenplay)
Actors: Vilma Santos, Jay Ilagan, Gina Alajar, Laurice Guillen
Plot: A nun becomes involved in an on-going labor strike. She starts out non-politicized, but later learns about the plight of the simple working man and inevitably, the government's neglect of the poor masses. Filipino Tagalog movie.
